n%20Sunday.%20With%20the%20series%20on%20the%20line%2C%20after%20both%20teams%20won%20two%20games%20apiece%20in%20the%20first%20four%20games%2C%20the%20deciding%20encounter%20was%20won%20by%20the%20hosts.%20Chasing%20a%20target%20of%20166%20runs%20set%20by%20the%20Indians%2C%20Windies%20had%2012%20balls%20to%20spare%20and%208%20wickets%20in%20hand%20as%20they%20succeeded%20in%20their%20mission.%20India%20captain%20Hardik%20admitted%20that%20his%20lack%20of%20rhythm%20and%20slow%20approach%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20as%20his%20team%20lost%20momentum%20during%20the%20back-10%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20under%20Pandya%20lost%20its%20first%20bilateral%20series%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%202-3%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20but%20the%20skipper%20harped%20on%20the%20positives%2C%20like%20the%20emergence%20of%20youngsters%20like%20Tilak%20Varma%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20the%20momentum%20when%20I%20came%20in%20and%20couldn't%20capitalize%20on%20the%20situation.%20I%20believe%20we%20gonna%20challenge%20ourselves.%20We%20try%20to%20get%20better.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20is%20fine.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20explain%20much.%20I%20know%20how%20the%20boys%20are%20within%20the%20group.%20We%20have%20enough%20time%20to%20figure%20out.%20Losing%20is%20good%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%2C%20we%20lost%20that%20period%20post%2010%20overs.%20Since%20when%20I%20came%2C%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20capitalise%20and%20I%20took%20my%20time%20and%20could%20not%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20slow%20track%2C%20Pandya%20defended%20his%20decision%20to%20bat%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20as%20a%20group%20we%20have%20to%20challenge%20ourselves.%20All%20these%20games%20are%20the%20games%20where%20we%20have%20to%20learn.%20We%20have%20spoken%20as%20a%20group%20that%20whenever%20we%20can%20take%20the%20hard%20way%20we%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20hindsight%2C%20one%20series%20here%20or%20there%20doesn't%20matter%20but%20the%20commitment%20to%20the%20goal%20is%20important.%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20knows%20that%20India%20will%20play%20World%20T20%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20world%20but%20doesn't%20want%20to%20look%20too%20far%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20long%20way.%20We%20have%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20coming%20up.%20And%20sometimes%20losing%20is%20good.%20You%20get%20to%20learn%20a%20lot.%20And%20special%20mention%20for%20all%20the%20boys.%20They%20showed%20great%20character.%20Winning%20and%20losing%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20learn%20from%20that.%26quot%3B%20Some%20of%20his%20bowling%20changes%20were%20called%20out%20by%20critics%20but%20he%20said%20that%20he%20goes%20by%20his%20instincts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20what%20I%20feel%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20don't%20plan%20much.%20If%20I%20see%20a%20situation%2C%20whatever%20my%20gut%20says%20I%20follow%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20praised%20Varma%20and%20Jaiswal%20for%20their%20lion-hearted%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20got%20heart.%20That%20is%20something%20that's%20very%20important%20in%20international%20cricket.%20Every%20youngster%20coming%20through%20has%20belief.%20That's%20something%20I%20see%20very%20often%20now.%20Kudos%20to%20them%2C%20they%20came%20out%20and%20took%20responsibility.%20I%20can't%20be%20happier%20as%20a%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691982060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fuvokmqt_hardik-pandya_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Flost-