r-beats-akshay-kumars-film-at-the-box-office%2Fphotostory%2F102701438.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Calls%20To%20Remove%20Nuh%20As%20Haryana%20District%2C%20Internet%20Back%20After%202%20Weeks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInternet%20services%20have%20been%20restored%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh%20where%20communal%20clashes%20broke%20out%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20leaving%20six%20people%20dead%20and%20several%20others%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%2C%20SMS%20and%20broadband%20services%20were%20suspended%20in%20Nuh%20in%20view%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btense%20and%20critical%26quot%3B%20situation%20after%20the%20July%2031%20clashes%20between%20two%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20started%20over%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20a%20religious%20procession%20that%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%2C%20including%20two%20Home%20Guards%20and%20a%20Mosque%20cleric%2C%20were%20killed%2C%20in%20the%20violence%20that%20later%20spilled%20over%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20Palwal%2C%20Faridabad%20and%20other%20districts%20of%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20vehicles%2C%20food%20joints%2C%20and%20shops%20were%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20unruly%20mobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumours%20that%20cow%20vigilante%20Monu%20Manesar%20would%20attend%20the%20religious%20procession%20in%20Nuh%20allegedly%20sparked%20the%20communal%20clashes%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManesar%20is%20said%20to%20have%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20social%20media%20in%20which%20he%20claimed%20to%20be%20attending%20the%20Nuh%20religious%20procession%20and%20called%20on%20his%20supporters%20to%20come%20out%20in%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cow%20vigilante%20said%20he%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20gathering%20at%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20which%20feared%20that%20his%20presence%20would%20create%20tensions%20in%20the%20