0Jerry%20Buss%20(John%20C.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22J.%20Kim%20Murphy%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwinning-time-jerry-buss-john-c-reilly-jeanie-hadley-robinson-1235695232%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwinning-time-jerry-buss-john-c-reilly-jeanie-hadley-robinson-1235695232%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwinning-time-jerry-buss-john-c-reilly-jeanie-hadley-robinson-1235695232%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22CCTVs%20Cannot%20Help%20In%20Stopping%20Ragging%2C%5C%22%20Jadavpur%20University%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudent%20leaders%20from%20Jadavpur%20University%20claimed%20that%20installing%20CCTV%20cameras%20on%20campus%20is%20not%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20to%20prevent%20incidents%20of%20ragging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCCTVs%20can%20only%20help%20in%20detecting%20who%20is%20the%20culprit.%20But%20CCTVs%20cannot%20help%20in%20stopping%20ragging%2C%26quot%3B%20Subhodeep%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Kolkata%20SFI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubstantiating%20their%20claim%2C%20another%20student%20leader%20questioned%20how%20effectively%20the%20Panchayat%20polls%20were%20conducted%20under%20CCTV%20cameras%20if%20they%20could%20prevent%20or%20solve%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20CCTVc%20violence%20took%20place%20during%20the%20West%20Bengal%20panchayat%20election.%20No%20arrests%20could%20be%20done%20based%20on%20their%20evidence.%20Nor%20can%20we%20say%20that%20the%20election%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20just%20manner.%20The%20narrative%20on%20bringing%20in%20CCTVs%20in%20the%20campus%20is%20being%20brought%20in%20now%20just%20to%20deviate%20from%20the%20main%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Aafrin%20Begum%2C%20state%20committee%20member%20of%20SFI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20the%20need%20that%20ex-students%20should%20vacate%20the%20hostel%2C%20Aafrin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20that%20many%20students%20who%20have%20passed%20out%20continue%20to%20stay%20in%20hostels.%20Even%20if%20authorities%20take%20action%20against%20them%2C%20they%20do%20not%20bother.%20Now%20after%20the%20incident%20hostellers%20are%20finally%20getting%20united%20against%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20the%20steps%20taken%20to%20curb%20ragging%2C%20Aafrin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUG1%20(Undergraduate%20first-year)%20students%20should%20be%20put%20in%20another%20hostel%20following%20UGC%20guildelines.%20The%20process%20has%20already%20begun.%20The%20list%20of%20pass-out%20students%20who%20are%20still%20staying%20in%20the%20hostel%20should%20be%20given%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20hostel%20supervisors%2C%20the%20student%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHostel%20supers%20(supervisors)%20have%20been%20kept%20on%20duty%20so%20that%20they%20can%20ensure%20that%20such%20kinds%20of%20incidents%20do%20not%20happen.%20How%20can%20they%20not%20know%20if%20a%20student%20falls%20down%3F%20How%20can%20they%20not%20know%20of%20incidents%20of%20ragging%3F%20How%20are%20they%20not%20aware%20of%20seniors%20who%20rag%20students%3F%20They%20(seniors)%20should%20be%20identified%2C%20interrogated%20and%20punished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegating%20the%20belief%20that%20ragging%20is%20a%20common%20practice%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%2C%20Aafrin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20organisation%20promotes%20ragging.%20We%20want%20all%20organisations%20in%20Jadavpur%20to%20get%20united%20against%20ragging.%20We%20are%2098%20per%20cent%20united%20that%20we%20will%20finish%20this.%20The%20two%20per%20cent%20are%20those%20who%20practice%20ragging%2C%20who%20frightens%20students%20to%20submit%20to%20ragging.%20We%20need%20to%20break%20those%20who%20want%20to%20keep%20this%20culture%20(of%20ragging)%20in%20the%20university.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20further%2C%20Subhodeep%20Bandyopadhyay%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20fair%20to%20blame%20the%20entire%20Jadavpur%20community%20for%20the%20incident%20of%20ragging.%20Ragging%20has%20become%20a%20culture%20for%20a%20few.%20However%2C%20we%20have%20stood%20against%20this%20ragging%20culture%20earlier%20and%20we%20will%20do%20so%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20We%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20union%20supports%20or%20promotes%20ragging.%20Those%20practising%20ragging%20are%20only%20a%20few%20individuals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Sunday%2C%20two%20more%20students%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20student%20death%20case%20taking%20the%20total%20number%20of%20arrests%20to%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first-year%20student%2C%20Swarnodip%20Kundu%2C%20of%20Jadavpur%20University%20in%20Kolkata%20died%20on%20Thursday%20after%20allegedly%20falling%20from%20the%20balcony%20of%20the%20university's%20hostel%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20Kundu%2C%20a%20first-year%20student%20of%20the%20Bengali%20Department%2C%20belonged%20to%20the%20state's%20Nadia%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691977740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fjadavpur-university_650x400_51466680900.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjadavpur-university-students-cctvs-cannot-help-in-stopping-ragging-4295466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Student%20leaders%20from%20Jadavpur%20University%20claimed%20that%20installing%20CCTV%20cameras%20on%20campus%20is%20not%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20to%20prevent%20incidents%20of%20ragging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find