0loved%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20despite%20its%20exaggerated%20versions%20of%20industry%20extremes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Schacter%20%E2%80%94%20a%2035-year-old%20director%20of%20public%20relations%20for%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Hotel%20Bangkok%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20first%20crossed%20paths%20in%20Bangkok%20in%20January%2C%20back%20when%20I%20was%20still%20working%20in%20public%20relations%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20a%20quiet%20corner%20of%20the%20Bang%20Rak%20district%2C%20we%20talked%20shop%20about%20the%20quirks%20and%20perks%20of%20our%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHearing%20about%20his%20work%20fascinated%20me%2C%20not%20just%20because%20he%20leads%20branding%20and%20engagement%20for%20one%20of%20the%20hotels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-thailand-resorts-filiming-spots-samui-bangkok-chiangmai-hbo-2023-3%5C%22%3Ewidely%20rumored%20to%20be%20the%20setting%20of%20the%20next%20season%20of%20the%20hit%20HBO%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20because%20of%20the%20unusual%20challenges%20that%20come%20with%20representing%20a%20luxury%20brand%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20those%20wondering%3A%20There's%20still%20no%20word%20on%20whether%20those%20rumors%20about%20the%20next%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20are%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Dan%20moved%20to%20Thailand%20in%202019%20and%20lives%20with%20his%20husband%20in%20Bangkok.%20Dan%20is%20also%20the%20regional%20director%20of%20public%20relations%20for%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20hotels%20and%20resorts%20for%20Asia-Pacific.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20most%20annoying%20misconceptions%20about%20your%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20about%20this%20job%20here%20in%20Thailand%20is%20that%20we're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bangkokpost.com%2Fthailand%2Fgeneral%2F2517290%2Fcall-for-govt-to-ban-sly-alcohol-ads%5C%22%3Enot%20allowed%20to%20promote%20alcohol%20and%20drinking%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20we're%20looking%20to%20promote%20a%20bar%2C%20we%20can't%20just%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BCome%20have%20a%20cocktail%20with%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221313%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20BKK%20Social%20Club%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Bangkok%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0ac7d20f1cf0019cbb7a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20BKK%20Social%20Club%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Hotel%20Bangkok.%3Cp%3EKen%20Seet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20be%20creative%20while%20adhering%20to%20the%20restrictions%20that%20come%20with%20operating%20in%20a%20Buddhist%20country.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20video%20ads%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20our%20bartenders'%20skills%20and%20the%20bar's%20inviting%20ambiance.%20We%20intentionally%20steer%20clear%20of%20showcasing%20alcohol%20labels%20or%20people%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20misconception%20is%20that%20Bangkok%20isn't%20just%20the%20cheap%20experience%20many%20perceive%20it%20to%20be.%20It%20has%20so%20much%20to%20offer%20and%20is%20gradually%20shedding%20the%20stereotype%20of%20being%20a%20cheap%20backpacker's%20city%20to%20being%20something%20that's%20more%20up-and-coming%20in%20the%20luxury%20scene%20%E2%80%94%20while%20still%20being%20great%20value%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20overcome%20the%20perception%20that%20Thailand's%20just%20a%20cheap%20destination%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20journalists%20that%20come%20through%20that%20have%20been%20here%20when%20they%20were%20just%20starting%20to%20travel%20in%20their%2020s.%20And%20now%20that%20it's%2010%20or%2020%20years%20later%2C%20and%20they're%20coming%20back%20to%20Bangkok%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%2C%20they're%20often%20very%20surprised%20about%20how%20things%20have%20evolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bangkok's%20Creative%20District%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0ae44f5d4870019e2c872%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBangkok's%20Creative%20District.%3Cp%3EKen%20Seet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Thailand%2C%20you%20can%20get%20a%20Michelin-star%20meal%20for%20%24100%2C%20while%20in%20the%20US%2C%20that%20might%20be%20a%20%24500%20meal.%20And%20that's%20what%20I%20think%20has%20become%20really%20interesting%20for%20these%20journalists.%20You're%20getting%20the%20quality%20and%20luxury%20but%20at%20really%20good%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJournalists%20wouldn't%20really%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20Bangkok's%20story%20of%20change%20unless%20we%20show%20them%20the%20hidden%20gems%20that%20may%20have%20gone%20unnoticed%20in%20their%20previous%20visits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Bangkok%20city%20street%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0acfdf5d4870019e2c7cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBangkok.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Mahon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20doing%20public%20relations%20for%20a%20hospitality%20giant%20changed%20your%20travel%20habits%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20Michael%2C%20and%20I%20have%20become%20more%20critical%20travelers%20in%20some%20ways%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hospitality.%20I%20think%20it's%20changed%20what%20we%20look%20for%20in%20a%20hotel%20or%20in%20a%20travel%20experience%2C%20and%20we've%20shifted%20more%20towards%20finding%20unique%20places%20to%20visit%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20Google%20searches%20or%20guides%20of%20major%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Schacter%20and%20his%20husband%20in%20a%20holiday%20in%20Bhutan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0b33120f1cf0019cbbb0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESchacter%20and%20his%20husband%20in%20a%20holiday%20in%20Bhutan.%3Cp%3EDan%20Schacter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20traveling%20in%20Hokkaido%20and%20Kyoto%20last%20winter%2C%20we%20were%20armed%20with%20a%20list%20of%20cool%2C%20little%20bars%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20shops%20from%20my%20colleagues%20in%20Japan%20and%20some%20travel%20journalists%20I%20met%20there%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recommended%20stops%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20Kaiseki%20lunch%20at%20Sakuragawa%20%E2%80%94%20ended%20up%20being%20our%20favorites%20in%20both%20cities%20and%20things%20we%20would%20have%20never%20found%20on%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20to%20ask%3A%20How%20has%20the%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20changed%20your%20job%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20our%20properties%20have%20been%20featured%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20first%20season%2C%20our%20Hawaii%20property%2C%20and%20then%20most%20recently%20in%20the%20Taormina%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20constantly%20being%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20as%20rumors%20spread%20that%20the%20next%20season%20might%20be%20in%20Thailand.%20As%20it's%20associated%20with%20HBO.%20There's%20obviously%20certain%20things%20we%20can%20and%20can't%20do%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20talking%20about%20it%2C%20but%20there's%20definitely%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20someone%20working%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%2C%20I%20absolutely%20loved%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciated%20the%20inclusion%20of%20queer%20representation%2C%20which%20felt%20authentic%20and%20meaningful%2C%20plus%20Jennifer%20Coolidge%20%E2%80%94%20always%20a%20gay%20icon%20but%20now%20brought%20more%20into%20the%20limelight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20I%20had%20slight%20concerns%20about%20how%20it%20might%20perpetuate%20certain%20misconceptions%20about%20luxury%20properties%2C%20it%20was%20entertaining%20to%20see%C2%A0exaggerated%20versions%20of%20some%20industry%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-seasons-thailand-bangkok-downsides-job-pr-director-white-lotus-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691976185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0a49a20f1cf0019cbb410%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-seasons-thailand-bangkok-downsides-job-pr-director-white-lotus-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dan%20Schacter%20leads%20branding%20and%20engagement%20for%20the%20hotels%20widely%20rumored%20to%20be%20the%20setting%20of%20the%20next%20season%20of%20the%20hit%20HBO%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A59%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-seasons-thailand-bangkok-downsides-job-pr-director-white-lotus-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20probe%20comes%20to%20end%20as%20Sebi%20tightens%20disclosure%20for%20big%20firms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691976135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F14%2Ffull%2F1691975779-7461.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompani