n%20their%20career.%20For%20young%20professionals%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20credibility%20game%20is%20still%20in%20its%20earliest%20stages%2C%26quot%3B%20Anders%20wrote.%20They%20could%20be%20trying%20to%20earn%20the%20trust%20and%20favor%20of%20managers%20by%20going%20the%20extra%20mile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennials%20and%20Gen%20Xers%20didn't%20fall%20far%20behind%20Gen%20Z%20on%20the%20scale%20of%20guilt.%20About%2030%25%20and%2032%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20felt%20guilt%20about%20not%20working%20while%20on%20vacation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20working%20year-round.%20Nearly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnearly-half-american-workers-dont-take-all-their-pto-research-2023-3%3F_gl%3D1*1813465*_ga*NDk0OTkwMDg3LjE2NTQ3MDM2MDA.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5MTk1MDQ4MC43MDEuMS4xNjkxOTUwNzE3LjYuMC4w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalf%20of%20Americans%20don't%20take%20all%20of%20their%20PTO%20day%3C%2Fa%3Es%2C%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20found.%20And%20only%20about%20half%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20surveyed%20by%20LinkedIn%20said%20they%20had%20planned%20a%20vacation%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuxury%20retail%20client%20advisor%20Razonie%20Napier%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20struggles%20with%20turning%20off%20his%20work%20phone%20when%20he's%20on%20vacation.%20The%2025-year-old%20said%20he%20often%20overthinks%20while%20he's%20away%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20industry%2C%20I%20do%20feel%20obligated%20to%20be%20available%20to%20my%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Napier%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20expect%20me%20to%20be%20there%20for%20them%20if%20they%20need%20an%20item%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20because%20it's%20my%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20loves%20his%20job%20helping%20clients%20find%20the%20right%20style%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20mind%20answering%20their%20c