20Forgot%20Her%20Bag%20At%20Airport%20Toilet%2C%20Then%20Help%20Arrived%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20nightmares%20for%20frequent%20fliers%20is%20the%20fear%20of%20losing%20an%20item%20or%20luggage%20at%20the%20airport.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20takes%20days%20and%20weeks%20for%20them%20to%20get%20the%20lost%20item%20back.%20However%2C%20a%20story%20of%20how%20a%20CISF%20officer%20promptly%20came%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%20a%20woman%20at%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%20is%C2%A0warming%20hearts%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghna%20Girish%20took%20to%20X%20and%20wrote%20that%20she%20left%20her%20handbag%20with%20her%20wallet%2C%20keys%2C%20and%20other%20important%20things%2C%20in%20the%20airport's%20washroom.%20Since%20she%20could%20not%20go%20back%20inside%2C%20a%20CISF%20officer%20came%20to%20her%20aid%20and%20assured%C2%A0her%20that%20she%20would%20get%20her%20bag%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20%23CISF%20officer%20first%20reassured%20me%20with%20'mil%20jayega%2C%20ek%20pin%20bhi%20yahan%20gum%20nahin%20hoga'%2C%20and%20while%20I%20had%20to%20wait%20outside%2C%20he%20got%20the%20%23Vistara%20ground%20staff%20to%20retrieve%20it%2C%20made%20sure%20my%20ID%20cards%20in%20the%20bag%20matched%20the%20boarding%20card%20on%20my%20phone....%20and%20grateful%20me%20sheepishly%20thanked%20them%20heaved%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20and%20took%20a%20cab%20home%2C''%20the%20tweet%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTuesdayThoughts%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TuesdayThoughts%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20past%20midnight%20when%20I%20tiredly%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20airport%20terminal....%20forgetting%20my%20handbag%20with%20house%20keys%2C%20wallet%20and%20all%20else%20in%20the%20wash%20room%20inside!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2