%20came%20over%20and%20handed%20me%20the%20purse%20after%20following%20me%20through%20cameras.%20Kudos%20to%20%23CISF.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691943240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8ela7sdo_cisf-officer_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-forgot-her-bag-with-wallet-at-airport-toilet-then-help-arrived-4295133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghna%20Girish%20took%20to%20X%20and%20wrote%20that%20she%20left%20her%20handbag%20with%20her%20wallet%2C%20keys%2C%20and%20other%20important%20things%2C%20in%20the%20airport's%20washroom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-forgot-her-bag-with-wallet-at-airport-toilet-then-help-arrived-4295133%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-forgot-her-bag-with-wallet-at-airport-toilet-then-help-arrived-4295133%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-forgot-her-bag-with-wallet-at-airport-toilet-then-help-arrived-4295133%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Record%20244%2C%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20Slams%20Another%20Century%20For%20Northamptonshire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20200%20in%20the%20previous%20match%2C%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20smashed%20a%20hundred%20to%20power%20Northamptonshire%20to%20a%20six-wicket%20victory%20over%20Durham%20in%20the%20One-Day%20Cup%20on%20Sunday.%20Giving%20another%20reminder%20of%20his%20striking%20powers%2C%20Shaw%20made%20an%20unbeaten%20125%20off%20just%2076%20balls%20with%2015%20fours%20and%20seven%20sixes.%20The%20Northants%20chased%20down%20a%20modest%20198%20with%20consummate%20ease.%20Pacer%20Luke%20Procter%20took%20four%20for%2034%20off%20nine%20overs%20as%20Northamptonshire%20restricted%20Durham%20to%20198%20in%2043.2%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPowered%20by%20opener%20Shaw's%20aggressive%20hundred%2C%20Northants%20overhauled%20the%20target%20in%20a%20mere%2025.4%20overs.%20Rob%20Keogh%20supported%20Shaw%20with%20a%2040-ball%2042%20in%20the%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20batter%20had%20made%20a%20magnificent%20244%20off%20153%20balls%20and%20that%20innings%20contained%2028%20boundaries%20and%2011%20sixes.%20In%20that%20match%2C%20Northamptonshire%20defeated%20Somerset%20by%2087%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaw%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20into%20the%20India%20side%20as%20the%20right-hander%20last%20played%20for%20India%20in%20a%20T20I%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaw%20had%20played%20for%20West%20Zone%20in%20the%20season%20opening%20Duleep%20Trophy%20last%20month%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691943120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fot3bi9b8_prithvi-shaw-northamptonshire-806_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-record-244-prithvi-shaw-slams-another-century-for-northamptonshire-4295099%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prithvi%20Shaw%20powered%20Northamptonshire%20to%20a%20six-wicket%20victory%20over%20Durham%20in%20the%20One-Day%20Cup%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A333%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-record-244-prithvi-shaw-slams-another-century-for-northamptonshire-4295099%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-record-244-prithvi-shaw-slams-another-century-for-northamptonshire-4295099%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-record-244-prithvi-shaw-slams-another-century-for-northamptonshire-4295099%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%9890%20Day%20Fianc%C3%A9%E2%80%99%20Casting%20Director%20On%20Recruiting%20the%20Spinoff%E2%80%99s%20First%20Transgender%20Woman%20and%20Deaf%20Person%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691942400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F90-Day-Fiance-Before-the-90-Days-David-Cleo-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235692454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reality%20hit%20%E2%80%9C90%20Day%20Fianc%C3%A9%E2%80%9D%20has%20grown%20into%20an%20entire%20industry%20for%20TLC%2C%20spawning%20countless%20spin-offs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20spin-offs%20of%20those%20spin-offs.%20The%20series%2C%20which%20premiered%20in%202014%2C%20quickly%20resonated%20with%20audiences%20who%20were%20fascinated%20by%20the%20premise%3A%20Under%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20K-1%20Visa%20process%2C%20in%20which%20an%20American%E2%80%99s%20fianc%C3%A9%20from%20another%20country%20moves%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22McKinley%20Franklin%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2F90-day-fiance-casting-trans-woman-deaf-person-1235692454%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2F90-day-fiance-casting-trans-woman-deaf-person-1235692454%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2F90-day-fiance-casting-trans-woman-deaf-person-1235692454%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dwarka%20Expressway%20Cost%2014%20Times%20More%20Than%20Sanctioned%2C%20Says%20Government%20Auditor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20highway%20built%20under%20the%20Centre's%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20phase-1%20has%20exceeded%20the%20amount%20approved%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20in%202017%20by%2014%20times%2C%20the%20government's%20top%20auditor%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20or%20CAG%20has%20found.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20report%20said%20the%20Expressway%2C%20prioritised%20to%20de-congest%20NH-48%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Gurugram%20by%20developing%20it%20into%20a%2014-lane%20national%20highway%20running%20parallelly%2C%20was%20built%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%26quot%3B%20per%20km%20cost%20of%20Rs%20250.77%20crore%20against%20the%20CCEA%20approved%20per%20km%20cost%20of%20Rs%2018.20%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highway's%20response%20on%20this%20from%20April%202022%2C%20saying%20the%20%26quot%3BDwarka%20Expressway%20was%20decided%20to%20be%20developed%20as%20an%20eight-lane%20elevated%20corridor%20with%20minimal%20entry%20exit%20arrangements%20to%20allow%20smooth%20movements%20of%20inter-state%20traffic%26quot%3B.%20This%20was%20cited%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20high%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20said%20there%20was%20no%20justification%20on%20record%20for%20planning%2Fconstruction%20of%20eight%20lanes%20(elevated%20lanes)%20for%20average%20daily%20traffic%20of%2055%2C432%20passenger%20vehicles.%20Only%20six%20lanes%20(at%20grade%20lanes)%20were%20planned%2Fconstructed%20for%20the%20average%20annual%20daily%20traffic%20of%202%2C32%2C959%20passenger%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20only%20highway%20with%20a%20mismatch%20of%20approved%20and%20actual%20costs.%20The%20report%20revealed%20that%20across%20India%2C%20the%20sanctioned%20cost%20under%20the%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20were%2058%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%20approved%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sanctioned%20cost%20of%2026%2C316%20km%20of%20project%20length%20was%20Rs%208%2C46%2C588%20crore%20(Rs%2032.17%20crore%2Fkm)%20as%20against%20CCEA%20approved%20length%20of%2034%2C800%20km%20at%20cost%20of%20Rs%205%2C35%2C000%20crore%20(Rs%2015.37%20crore%2Fkm).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20increasing%20cost%2C%20the%202022%20deadline%20for%20completing%2034%2C800%20km%20of%20national%20highways%20has%20not%20been%20met.%20Only%2013%2C499%20km%20of%20national%20highways%20length%20has%20been%20completed%20till%2031%20March%202023%2C%20which%20is%2038.79%20per%20cent%20of%20CCEA%20approved%20length.%20This%20includes%20the%20construction%20undertaken%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20stark%20increase%20in%20costs%2C%20the%20report%20said%20significant%20changes%20were%20made%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20projects%20and%20cost%20estimates.%20Also%2C%20richer%20project%20specifications%20adopted%20have%20pushed%20up%20the%20sanctioned%20cost%20of%20projects%20awarded%20under%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20Phase%201.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20cost%20increase%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20per%20km%20of%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20need%20for%20more%20funds%2C%20funds%20approved%20for%20other%20schemes%20(Rs%201%2C57%2C324%20crore)%20were%20being%20utilised.%20So%20far%2C%2078%20such%20projects%20(1%2C752%20km%20taken%20together)%20approved%20under%20other%20schemes%2C%20were%20being%20reported%20as%20achievements%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20Phase-1%20as%20on%2031%20March%202023%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancies%20didn't%20just%20exist%20in%20fund%20management.%20Even%20the%20appraisal%20and%20approval%20mechanisms%20decided%20by%20CCEA%20were%20also%20not%20strictly%20followed%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAG%20said%20here%20were%20cases%20of%20successful%20bidders%20not%20fulfilling%20tender%20condition%20or%20bidders%20being%20selected%20on%20basis%20of%20falsified%20documents.%20Work%20has%20been%20awarded%20without%20there%20being%20approved%20detailed%20project%20reports%20or%20was%20based%20on%20faulty%20detailed%20project%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20implementing%20agencies%20were%20still%20awarding%20projects%20without%20ensuring%20availability%20of%20requisite%20land%2C%20resulting%20in%20delayed%20commencement%20of%20projects%20construction%20and%20their%20completion.%20Also%2C%20many%20Bharatmala%20projects%20were%20being%20implemented%20without%20environmental%20clearance%20in%20contravention%20of%20prescribed%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20safety%20consultants%20too%20were%20not%20ensured%20at%20all%20stages%20of%20construction.%20Due%20to%20wrong%20computation%20of%20price-adjustment%20formula%20in%20case%20of%20some%20projects%2C%20contractors%2Fconcessionaires%20were%20paid%20excess%20price%20adjustments%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2099.16%20crore.%20There%20was%20diversion%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%2C598.52%20crore%20from%20escrow%20accounts%20for%20HAM%2FBOT%20projects%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20report%20added%20that%20the%20pace%20of%20per%20day%20project%20length%20constructed%20under%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20has%20improved%20from%201.04%20km%20in%202018-19%20to%2012.37%20km%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20CAG%20report%2C%20released%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20said%20toll%20rules%20have%20been%20violated%20across%20several%20states%20in%20south%20India%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20undue%20burden%20of%20Rs%20154%20crores%20on%20road%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20non-implementation%20of%20NH%20Fee%20Amendment%20Rules%202013%2C%20NHAI%20continued%20to%20collect%20user%20fee%20in%20three%20toll%20plazas%20(namely%20Nathavalasa%2C%20Chalageri%2C%20Hebbalu)%20during%20delayed%20period%20of%20construction%20though%20the%20amended%20rule%20said%20no%20user%20fee%20shall%20be%20levied%20for%20the%20delayed%20period.%20The%20road%20users%20continued%20to%20pay%20user%20fee%20during%20the%20delayed%20period%20of%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691942340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fgtjirapo_dwarka-expressway_625x300_19_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-cost-14-times-more-than-sanctioned-says-government-auditor-4295039%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cost%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20highway%20built%20under%20the%20Centre's%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20phase-1%20has%20exceeded%20the%20amount%20approved%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20in%202017%20by%2014%20times%2C%20the%20government's%20top%20auditor%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-cost-14-times-more-than-sanctioned-says-government-auditor-4295039%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-cost-14-times-more-than-sanctioned-says-government-auditor-4295039%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-cost-14-times-more-than-sanctioned-says-government-auditor-4295039%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi's%20emotional%20note%20for%20mom%20Sridevi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691941576000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102701173%2Cimgsize-97286.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjanhvi-kapoor-pens-emotional-note-for-sridevi-on-her-birthday-reveals-her-most-favourite-place-to-be%2Farticleshow%2F102701165.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102701165.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJanhvi%20Kapoor%20pens%20emotional%20note%20for%20her%20mother%20Sridevi%20on%20her%20birthday.%20The%20actress%20shared%20a%20throwback%20picture%20of%20Sridevi%20with%20her%20mother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0