0disasters%2C%20adverse%20weather%2C%20and%20invasive%20diseases%20have%20all%20helped%20wreak%20havoc%20on%20the%20market%20for%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20foodstuffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20succession%20of%20hurricanes%20and%20deadly%20bacteria%20have%20ravaged%20American%20oranges%2C%20while%20heavy%20rainfall%20has%20rotted%20cacao%20beans%20in%20West%20Africa.%20As%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20Asian%20rice%20hit%20its%20highest%20price%20in%20almost%2015%20years%3B%20while%20in%20China%2C%20pork%20prices%20have%20slumped%20so%20far%20that%20they%20have%20dragged%20inflation%20into%20negative%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20roundup%20of%20what's%20been%20happening%20in%20the%20world%20of%20soft%20commodities%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrange%20juice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOrange%20juice%20futures%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20on%20July%2028%2C%20as%20citrus%20crops%20all%20across%20the%20US%20have%20been%20hammered%20by%20a%20series%20of%20hurricanes%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20'citrus%20greening'%2C%20an%20incurable%20disease%20spread%20by%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICE%20US%20frozen%20orange%20futures%20index%C2%A0touched%20a%20record%20317.5%20(USc%20per%20lb)%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20metric%20that%20reflects%20orange%20juice%20production%20in%20the%20US%20as%20the%20lowest%20in%20%26quot%3Bover%20100%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20Matthew%20Joyner%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Florida%20Citrus%20Mutual%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fab06eadb-1de6-45e8-89c7-50531614d9a8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20oranges%20produced%20in%20the%20US%20come%20from%20Florida%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hobbled%20by%20hurricanes%20and%20a%20cold%20snap%2C%20massively%20hampering%20supply.%20Not%20only%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%2C%20but%20the%20resurgence%20of%20the%20pathogen%2C%C2%A0%20has%20ravaged%20crops%20in%20both%20America%20and%20Brazil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20headwinds%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20supply%20shortage%20in%20oranges%2C%20which%20has%20driven%20up%20prices%20that%20will%20eventually%20filter%20through%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChinese%20pork%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fchina-pork-prices-have-fallen-dragging-country-into-deflation-2023-8%5C%22%3EChinese%20pork%20prices%20have%20fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20over%20a%20quarter%20since%20the%20previous%20July%20as%20an%20oversupply%20of%20meat%20has%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20consumer%20food%20prices%2C%20pushing%20the%20Asian%20state%20into%20a%20period%20of%20deflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPork%20plays%20an%20important%20part%20in%20the%20makeup%20of%20China's%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20basket%2C%20accounting%20for%20around%203%25%20of%20it%2C%20per%20the%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit.%20%26quot%3BA%20rough%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20therefore%20that%20a%2010%25%20increase%20in%20the%20pork%20price%20will%20push%20up%20the%20CPI%20by%200.3%25%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountry.eiu.com%2Farticle.aspx%3Farticleid%3D636856447%26Country%3DChina%26topic%3DEconomy%26oid%3D1092669893%26flid%3D357283419%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20EIU%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20research%20note%2C%20underscoring%20the%20animal's%20importance%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%20showed%20that%20pork%20prices%20have%20fallen%2026%25%20in%20July%20year-on-year%2C%20a%20significant%20fall%20for%20the%20world's%20largest%20producer%20and%20consumer%20of%20the%20meat.%20The%20decline%20in%20prices%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20oversupply%20in%20the%20market%2C%20caused%20by%20a%20backlog%20after%20a%20bad%20outbreak%20of%20African%20swine%20fever.%C2%A0%