%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66490857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66490857.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66490857.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arunachali%20Anti-Dam%20Activist%20Ebo%20Mili%20Detained%20for%20Protesting%20Against%20Signing%20of%20Hydropower%20Projects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13140137%2Fimage-1220.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20anti-dam%20activist%20and%20advocate%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Ebo%20Mili%2C%20was%20detained%20by%20the%20state%20police%20on%20August%2012%2C%20along%20with%20a%20colleague%2C%20for%20staging%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20outside%20a%20banquet%20hall%20in%20Itanagar%2C%20where%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20was%20engaged%20in%20signing%20memoranda%20of%20understanding%20(MoAs)%20with%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20(PSUs)%20to%20unroll%2012%20stalled%20hydropower%20projects%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F08%2F13%2Fanti-dam-activist-ebo-mili-prevented-from-staging-peaceful-protest-forced-to-sign-bond%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20chief%20minister%20Pema%20Khandu%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Chowna%20Mein%2C%20the%20signing%20ceremony%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Union%20minister%20for%20power%20and%20new%20and%20renewable%20energy%20R.K.%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%20that%20while%20the%20police%20denied%20they%20were%20detained%20but%20state%20capital%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Rohit%20Rajbir%20Singh%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20team%20patrolling%20the%20Niti%20Vihar%20area%20chanced%20upon%20advocate%20Ebo%20Mili%2C%20who%20had%20come%20to%20voice%20his%20opinions%20on%20the%20dam%20subject.%20He%20and%20his%20colleague%20Mejo%20Mihu%20were%20then%20enquired%20regarding%20the%20action.%20They%20will%20shortly%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20their%20well-wishers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20learnt%20that%2C%20after%20hours-long%20interrogation%2C%20Mili%20and%20Mihu%20were%20reportedly%20forced%20by%20the%20police%20to%20sign%20a%20bond%20and%20they%20were%20later%20taken%20to%20the%20ICR%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office.%E2%80%9D%20His%20well-wishers%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20harassing%20them%20for%20protesting%20against%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20made%20them%20stand%20for%20hours%20at%20the%20police%20station%20and%20unnecessarily%20harassed%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20Mili%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farunachal-activist-assam-graffiti-artist-arrested-for-protest-artwork-on-govt-buildings%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20state%20police%20along%20with%20an%20Assam-based%20artist%2C%20Nilim%20Mahanta%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20defacing%20a%20mural%20of%20a%20dam%20drawn%20on%20the%20boundary%20wall%20of%20the%20state%20secretariat%20by%20placing%20a%20resistance%20logo%20and%20writing%20%E2%80%98No%20More%20Dams%E2%80%99%20in%20black.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20go-ahead%20of%20the%20BJP%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20and%20at%20the%20Centre%20to%20the%20stalled%20dam%20projects%20in%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20north-eastern%20state%20is%20likely%20to%20generate%20about%2011%2C523%20megawatt%20of%20energy%20cumulatively.%20Five%20projects%20(2%2C626%20MW)%20have%20been%20allocated%20to%20the%20North%20Eastern%20Electric%20Power%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(NEEPCO)%2C%20five%20projects%20(5%2C097%20MW)%20to%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20(SJVN)%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20two%20projects%20(3%2C800%20MW)%20to%20the%20National%20Hydroelectric%20Power%20Corporation%20(NHPC)%2C%20as%20per%20another%20report%20on%20the%20newspaper.%20These%20dams%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F08%2F13%2Fgoap-signs-moas-with-psus-to-develop-12-stalled-heps%2F%5C%22%3Eare%20expected%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20up%20on%20the%20Lohit%2C%20Subansiri%20Dibang%20and%20Siang%20river%20basins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20of%20dams%20in%20the%20border%20state%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue.%20Several%20protest%20movements%20have%20been%20seen%20by%20the%20local%20population%20to%20resist%20dam%20construction%20including%20in%20Tawang%20where%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20involved%20in%20dam%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20editorial%20on%20August%2012%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Acheso%20Atih%20Welfare%20Society%20(AAWA)%20had%20opposed%20signing%20of%20the%20MoA%20with%20the%20SJVN%20for%20the%20420%20MW%20Mihundo%20HEP%2C%20and%20the%20All%20Idu%20Mishmi%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20had%20declared%20a%2012-hour%20bandh%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20against%20signing%20of%20the%20MoAs%20in%20Dibang%20valley%20and%20Lower%20Dibang%20valley%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20locals%20are%20alleging%20that%20their%20concerns%20had%20not%20been%20addressed%20before%20the%20signing%20of%20MoAs.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20allegation.%20The%20government%20should%20have%20taken%20locals%20into%20confidence%20before%20signing%20MoAs.%20Hydropower%20is%20a%20very%20sensitive%20subject%20and%20deeply%20emotional%20too.%20A%20large%20section%20of%20the%20people%20do%20not%20want%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20their%20land.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20government%20will%20look%20into%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20affected%20people.%20They%20should%20engage%20in%20a%20dialogue%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2