f%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20through%20a%20sweeping%20overhaul%E2%80%9D%20which%20%E2%80%9Creeks%20of%20linguistic%20imperialism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRecolonisation%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Recolonisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDecolonisation%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Decolonisation%3C%2Fa%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audacious%20attempt%20by%20the%20Union%20BJP%20Government%20to%20tamper%20with%20the%20essence%20of%20India's%20diversity%20through%20a%20sweeping%20overhaul%20%E2%80%93%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%20and%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20reeks%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUTSs9AtUGW%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUTSs9AtUGW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20M.K.Stalin%20(%40mkstalin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkstalin%2Fstatus%2F1689959429096271872%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20very%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity.%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20have%20no%20moral%20right%20to%20even%20utter%20the%20word%20Tamil%20hereafter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fire%20of%20resistance%20against%20%23HindiColonialism%20is%20ablaze%20once%20more.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20audacious%20bid%20to%20supplant%20our%20identity%20with%20Hindi%20will%20be%20opposed%20resolutely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20for%20education%20and%20skill%20development%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan