nity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%20another%20own-goal%20by%20the%20petty%20minds%20in%20the%20BJP!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20348%20(b)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F928281%2F%5C%22%3Estates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20Bills%20or%20amendments%20to%20be%20moved%20in%20either%20House%20of%20parliament%20or%20state%20legislature%2C%20all%20acts%20passed%20by%20parliament%20or%20state%20legislatures%2C%20ordinances%20passed%20by%20the%20President%20or%20state%20governors%2C%20and%20all%20orders%2C%20rules%2C%20regulations%20and%20bye%20laws%20issued%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20under%20any%20law%20made%20by%20Parliament%20or%20the%20Legislature%20of%20a%20State%2C%20shall%20be%20in%20the%20English%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20adds%20that%20in%20the%20instance%20of%20laws%20being%20made%20by%20state%20legislatures%20in%20any%20other%20Indian%20language%2C%20a%20translation%20needs%20to%20be%20available%20of%20the%20text%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20DMK%20MP%20P.%20Wilson%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20move%20to%20name%20the%20new%20Bills%20in%20Hindi%20is%20%E2%80%9Cyet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShocked%20to%20see%20names%20of%20new%20IPC%2C%20CrPC%20and%20Evidence%20Act%20in%20Hindi.%20Maybe%20the%20Hon.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20has%20not%20seen%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%3F%20Names%20of%20Bills%20%26amp%3B%20Acts%20must%20be%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20yet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%20South%20Indian%20lawyers%20are%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTuXAjqpcdL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTuXAjqpcdL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20P.%20