ia%2C%20Blue%20Cross%2C%20and%20Besant%20Memorial%20Animal%20Dispensary.%20She%20also%20began%20working%20with%20the%20Western%20Ghat%20Wildlife%20Conservation%20Trust%20(WGWCT)%20where%20she%20continues%20to%20work%20as%20the%20chief%20co-ordinator%20for%20Chennai%20and%20the%20wildlife%20management%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department%2C%20Vedhapriya%20is%20often%20called%20on%20for%20wildlife%20rescues.%20She%20says%20she%20has%20rescued%20more%20than%206%2C000%20snakes%20so%20far%20and%20recounts%20a%20rescue%20where%20a%20child%20was%20stuck%20inside%20a%20house%20with%20a%20snake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20couple%20who%20stayed%20in%20a%20nearby%20street%20came%20running%20to%20my%20house%20one%20day.%20A%20snake%20had%20entered%20their%20house%20where%20their%20infant%20was%20playing.%20About%2050%20people%20were%20standing%20outside%20but%20no%20one%20was%20able%20to%20help%20the%20baby.%20When%20I%20entered%20the%20house%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20the%20snake%20was%20busy%20trying%20to%20eat%20a%20lizard%20and%20the%20baby%20was%20happily%20playing.%20I%20caught%20the%20snake%20after%20it%20ate%20the%20lizard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20snakes%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F193230%2Fkerala-woman-snake-rescuer-breaks-stereotypes-kochi-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20rescuer%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20monkeys%2C%20black%20kites%2C%20and%20other%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20the%20forest%20department%20officials%20are%20busy%2C%20they%20ask%20us%20to%20go%20for%20the%20rescues.%20I%20also%20conduct%20training%20sessions%20for%20the%20fire%20department%20officials%20along%20with%20various%20awareness%20programmes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-